org.dspace.eperson.dao.impl

Class EPersonDAOImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.core.AbstractHibernateDAO<T>
      • org.dspace.core.AbstractHibernateDSODAO<EPerson>
        • org.dspace.eperson.dao.impl.EPersonDAOImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DSpaceObjectDAO<EPerson>, DSpaceObjectLegacySupportDAO<EPerson>, GenericDAO<EPerson>, EPersonDAO

    public class EPersonDAOImpl
extends AbstractHibernateDSODAO<EPerson>
implements EPersonDAO
    Hibernate implementation of the Database Access Object interface class for the EPerson object. This class is responsible for all database calls for the EPerson object and is autowired by spring This class should never be accessed directly.
    Author:
    kevinvandevelde at atmire.com
